<paragraph id="AE7DEC43F773FFE1FF25F89D438CF88C" blockId="51.[151,1436,1741,1938]" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">
Remarks: According to descriptions, 
<taxonomicName id="69C297C0F773FFE1FD86F89E45F6F8AB" authorityName="Soto-Adames &amp; Giordano" authorityYear="2011" box="[623,721,1842,1865]" class="Entognatha" family="Isotomidae" genus="Bellisotoma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Collembola" pageId="51" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="joycei">
<emphasis id="9CB63051F773FFE1FD86F89E45F6F8AB" box="[623,721,1842,1865]" italics="true" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">B. joycei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is very similar to 
<taxonomicName id="69C297C0F773FFE1FC77F89E432FF8AB" box="[926,1032,1842,1865]" class="Entognatha" family="Isotomidae" genus="Proisotoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Collembola" pageId="51" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ewingi">
<emphasis id="9CB63051F773FFE1FC77F89E432FF8AB" box="[926,1032,1842,1865]" italics="true" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">B. ewingi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and as stressed by 
<bibRefCitation id="CA5391B2F773FFE1FB01F89D47D8F88C" author="Soto-Adames" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Soto-Adames" pageId="51" pageNumber="52" pagination="7 - 13" refId="ref90453" refString="Soto-Adames, F. N., Giordano, R. &amp; Christiansen, K. (2013) Bellisotoma, a new genus of Isotomidae from North America (Hexapoda, Collembola). ZooKeys, 283, 7 - 13. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.3897 / zookeys. 283.3277" type="journal article" year="2013">
Soto-Adames 
<emphasis id="9CB63051F773FFE1FA61F89E4793F88C" italics="true" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">et al.</emphasis>
(2013
</bibRefCitation>
, p. 12), “it is possible that James species [
<taxonomicName id="69C297C0F773FFE1FD3FF8FA4406F88F" box="[726,801,1878,1901]" class="Entognatha" family="Isotomidae" genus="Proisotoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Collembola" pageId="51" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ewingi">
<emphasis id="9CB63051F773FFE1FD3FF8FA4406F88F" box="[726,801,1878,1901]" italics="true" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">ewingi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
] is a senior synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="69C297C0F773FFE1FBDFF8FA43BFF88F" authorityName="Soto-Adames &amp; Giordano" authorityYear="2011" box="[1078,1176,1878,1901]" class="Entognatha" family="Isotomidae" genus="Bellisotoma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Collembola" pageId="51" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="joycei">
<emphasis id="9CB63051F773FFE1FBDFF8FA43BFF88F" box="[1078,1176,1878,1901]" italics="true" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">B. joycei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
”.
</paragraph>
